Say '''Siruma''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Camarines Sur]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 17,050 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 141.27 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumapat ya distrito. Say zip code to et 4427.	
															
